pidgin-indicator: Ubuntu Indicator Plugin for Pidgin
====================================================

0.6 (??):
---------

* Fixed focusing of conversation tabs when going to
  unread conversations.
* Enabled translations.

0.5 (2014-01-14):
-----------------

Initial release.

Fully functional, with one exception:
* Plugin Action menu items are not refreshed.
  You must restart pidgin or reload the plugin
  to update these menu items.
